<br>
If you are going hardcore...do the following:<br>
<br>
Get a golem wand from Cazic. (maybe even two/three)Blast him with it. (Rangers are very buff dependent) Also get your Fr up, he might try to nuke you.<br>
<br>
Get damage shield potions for yourself, as rangers often dont max their two handed slashing. <br>
<br>
Get all the clickable healing items you can. <br>
<br>
Stick to him like glue. Dont let him get a heal off. Learn how to backstab on the run.<br>
<br>
Disarm/Disarm/Disarm! ID/ID/ID!  Rangers suck at these.   <br>
<br>
Get regen items it you can.<br>
<br>
Those tactics should help alot. <br>
<br>
